{"tid":2184412,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果發現女朋友做PTGF，即刻分手絕對係最愚蠢既做法！","createTime":"2020-09-01T13:45:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T17:05:10.000Z","uid":209657,"like":487,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"698db3d21ece5a3a2bee54c2946983be1f80472b","tid":2184412,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T13:45:12.000Z","msg":"你女朋友俾你（or人地）發現左嗰刻，心靈一定好脆弱，好傷心，希望你原諒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。你只要你表達你好愛佢，反過來安慰佢，屌9嗰啲笑你女朋友既人，公開表示不離不棄！呢件事過左之後佢只會更愛你，唔想你離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，之後佢起碼會安份守己一排，身體屬於你一個人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n橫掂都已經綠左咁耐，不如綠埋落去，反正點計都係你贏！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你諗下，你唔洗俾錢就可以約佢睇戲食飯殘廁中出3p，體驗下啲&ldquo;女朋友&rdquo;唔會做既野！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相反，你即刻飛左佢，坐喺屋企打飛機咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？你唔要人地，人地又可以搵第個開心，咁咪會俾人執雞囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！你有target之後，或者玩厭先再飛都唔遲啦！所以話，英華仔真係識玩！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52287780ac23f6f209eddfc32c56efacfebd2e02","tid":2184412,"uid":343361,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T13:46:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ce83aa3228015294c6b48120ae97816388977c9","tid":2184412,"uid":9392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T13:51:58.000Z","msg":"......."},{"pid":"4286f9cca9d932c8be70c2adaa270a39d7fb8209","tid":2184412,"uid":21141,"like":265,"dislike":1,"score":264,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T14:00:23.000Z","msg":"叫佢做ftgf養埋你好冇，反正佢人工點都高過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fafc465e1c6edfd0525922d0f06e66576ff6ae62","tid":2184412,"uid":209657,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"quote":{"pid":"4286f9cca9d932c8be70c